    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require moped/motorcycle making delivers to have a full licence",
        "additional_details": "Many delivery drivers use vehicles with L plates and I have seen many driving recklessly, which endangers other road users, pedestrians and themselves. Please pass legislation to stop people making deliveries using mopeds and motorcycles with L plates.",
        "background": "We want the Government to require drivers using mopeds and motorcycles for deliveries - such as Uber Eats and Deliveroo drivers - to be required to have a full licence.",
